short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension with handy utilities for Osano employees and customers to enjoy.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Osano browser extension allows you to test Osano Consent Management Platform (CMP) cookie banners on any website without editing backend code. You must have an Osano customer account to make use of this extension.
